        <div n="998-CWJS">
          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-998-CWJS-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-998-CWJS-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-998-CWJS-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">&#13;</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-998-CWJS-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-998-CWJS-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-998-CWJS-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-998-CWJS-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-998-CWJS-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-998-CWJS-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-1" n="1">
              <hi rend="display-initial">Y<hi rend="small-caps">OU</hi> say your Face is better hung</hi>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-2" n="2">Than ours──By what? by Nose or Tongue?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-3" n="3">In not explaining you were wrong</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-4" n="4">«LD»to us Sir?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-5" n="5">Because we thus must state the Case,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-6" n="6">That you have got a hanging Face,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-7" n="7">Th' untimely End's a damn'd Disgrace</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-8" n="8">«LD»of Noose Sir.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-9" n="9">But yet be not cast down, I see</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-10" n="10">A Weaver will your Hangman be,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-11" n="11">You'll only hang in Tapestry</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-12" n="12">«LD»with many.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-13" n="13">And then the Ladies, I suppose,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-14" n="14">Will praise your Longitude of Nose,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-15" n="15">For latent Charms within your Cloaths,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-16" n="16">
              <space>dear <hi rend="italics">Danny</hi>/hi&gt;.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-17" n="17">Thus will the Fair of ev'ry Age,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-18" n="18">From all Parts make their Pilgrimage,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-19" n="19">Worship thy Nose with pious Rage</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-20" n="20">«LD»of Love Sir.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-21" n="21">All their Religion will be spent</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-22" n="22">About thy woven Monument,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-23" n="23">And not one Orison be sent</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-24" n="24">
              <space>to <hi rend="italics">Jove</hi>/hi&gt; Sir.</space>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-25" n="25">You the fam'd Idol will become,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-26" n="26">As Gardens grac'd in ancient <hi rend="italics">Rome</hi>,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-27" n="27">By Matrons worshipp'd in the Gloom</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-28" n="28">«LD»of Night.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-29" n="29">O happy <hi rend="italics">Dan</hi>! thrice happy sure!</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-30" n="30">Thy Fame for ever shall endure,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-31" n="31">Who after Death can love secure</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-32" n="32">«LD»at Sight.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-33" n="33">So far I thought it was my Duty</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-34" n="34">To dwell upon thy boasted Beauty;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-35" n="35">Now I'll proceed a Word or two t'ye,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-36" n="36">«LD»in Answer</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-37" n="37">To that Part where you carry on</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-38" n="38">This Paradox, that Rock and Stone,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-39" n="39">In your Opinion are all one.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-40" n="40">«LD»How can, Sir,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-41" n="41">A Man of Reas'ning so profound,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-42" n="42">So stupidly be run aground,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-43" n="43">As things so different to confound</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-44" n="44">«LD»t'our Senses?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-45" n="45">Except you judg'd 'em by the Knock</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-46" n="46">Of near an equal hardy Block,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-47" n="47">Such an experimental Stroak</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-48" n="48">«LD»convinces.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-49" n="49">Then might you be, by Dint of Reason,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-50" n="50">A proper Judge on this Occasion;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-51" n="51">'Gainst Feeling there's no Disputation,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-52" n="52">«LD»is granted.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-53" n="53">Therefore to thy superior Wit,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-54" n="54">Who made the Trial, we submit,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-55" n="55">Thy Head to prove the Truth of it</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-56" n="56">«LD»we wanted.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-57" n="57">In one Assertion you're to blame,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-58" n="58">Where <hi rend="italics">Dan</hi> and <hi rend="italics">Sherry</hi>'s made the same,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-59" n="59">Endeavouring to have your Name</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-60" n="60">«LD»refin'd Sir.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-61" n="61">You'll see most grosly you mistook,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-62" n="62">If you consult your Spelling-Book,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-63" n="63">(The better Half you say you took)</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-64" n="64">«LD»you'll find Sir,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-65" n="65">S, H, E, <hi rend="italics">She</hi>──and R, I, <hi rend="italics">ri</hi>,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-66" n="66">Both put together make <hi rend="italics">Sherry</hi>,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-67" n="67">D, A, N, <hi rend="italics">Dan</hi>──makes up the three</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-68" n="68">«LD»Syllables.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-69" n="69"><hi rend="italics">Dan</hi> is but one, and <hi rend="italics">Sherri</hi> two,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-70" n="70">Then, Sir, your Choice will never do,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-71" n="71">Therefore I've turn'd, my Friend, on you</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-998-CWJS-line-72" n="72">«LD»the Tables.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
